{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource\/featuresmatchingpredicate:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"featuresMatchingPredicate:"}],"title":"featuresMatchingPredicate:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNShapeSource(im)featuresMatchingPredicate:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"featuresMatchingPredicate:","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns an array of map features for this source, filtered by the given"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"predicate."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray<id<MLNFeature>>"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"featuresMatchingPredicate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSPredicate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSPredicate"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"predicate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"predicate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A predicate to filter the returned features. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"include all features in the source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","level":2,"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An array of objects conforming to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"represent features in the source that match the predicate.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Each object in the returned array represents a feature for the current style","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and provides access to attributes specified via the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Features come from tiled GeoJSON data that is converted to tiles internally,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so feature geometries are clipped at tile boundaries and features","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"may appear duplicated across tiles. For example, suppose this source contains a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"long polyline representing a road. The resulting array includes those parts of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the road that lie within the map tiles that the source has loaded, even if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"road extends into other tiles. The portion of the road within each map tile is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"included individually.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Returned features may not necessarily be visible to the user at the time they"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are loaded: the style may lack a layer that draws the features in question. To"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"obtain only "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"visible"}]},{"type":"text","text":" features, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"